<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7797baa6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s430uu–4"><num value="430uu–4">§ 430uu–4.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums not exceeding $42,500 as are necessary for the acquisition of lands and interests in land pursuant to sections 430uu to 430uu–4 of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7797baa7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/88/24/s5">Pub. L. 88–24, § 5</ref>, <date date="1963-05-17">May 17, 1963</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/77/19">77 Stat. 19</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/92/272/tI/s101/2">Pub. L. 92–272, title I, § 101(2)</ref>, <date date="1972-04-11">Apr. 11, 1972</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/86/120">86 Stat. 120</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
