<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7797baaa-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1972—<ref href="/us/pl/92/272">Pub. L. 92–272</ref> substituted “$42,500” for “$20,000”.</p>
